{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/dev/web/req_res","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"959d6e4a-85f1-5805-a763-053006f32d89","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"http-의-첫번째-특징\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EC%9D%98-%EC%B2%AB%EB%B2%88%EC%A7%B8-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\" aria-label=\"http 의 첫번째 특징 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 의 첫번째 특징,</h2>\n<h1 id=\"요청과-응답-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9A%94%EC%B2%AD%EA%B3%BC-%EC%9D%91%EB%8B%B5-\" aria-label=\"요청과 응답  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>요청과 응답 !</h1>\n<p><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"http-는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"http 는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 는</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Client 의 Request!\n\nServer 의 Response!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">위의 두가지 통신내용에 대한 규약이에요.</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"구성요소는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"구성요소는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구성요소는</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Start Line\n - 해당 통신에 대한 정보\n\nHeader\n - 통신내용의 개요\n\nBody\n - 실제 통신의 내용</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">이렇게, 크게 세 부분으로 나뉘어 구성되어 있어요.</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"start-line-의-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#start-line-%EC%9D%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"start line 의 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Start Line 의 구성</h2>\n<h3 id=\"--request\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--request\" aria-label=\"  request permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Request</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- HTTP Method\n    : 해당 통신이 의도한 Action\n\n- Request Target\n    : 요청의 대상이 되는 URI\n\n- HTTP Version\n    : 사용된 HTTP 버젼</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"--response\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--response\" aria-label=\"  response permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Response</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- HTTP version\n    : 사용된 HTTP 버젼\n\n- Status code\n    : 응답 상태를 나타내는 코드\n\n- Status text\n    : 응답 상태를 간략하게 설명하는 문장</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Response 의 Start Line 은\n\nStatus Line 이라고 불려요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"header-의-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#header-%EC%9D%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"header 의 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Header 의 구성</h2>\n<h3 id=\"--request-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--request-1\" aria-label=\"  request 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Request</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- General\n    : Via, Connection 등의 항목\n\n- Request\n    : 헤더로써 요청의 내용을 구체화 시키는 항목\n\n- Entity\n    : 본문이 적용된 내용에 관련된 항목</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"이런-값들이-있어요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%9F%B0-%EA%B0%92%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9E%88%EC%96%B4%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"이런 값들이 있어요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이런 값들이 있어요!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Accept : 클라이언트가 받을 수 있는 컨텐츠\nCookie : 쿠키\nContent-Type : 메세지 바디 종류\nContent-Length : 메세지 바디 길이\nAuthorization : 인증과 관련된 내용</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"--response-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--response-1\" aria-label=\"  response 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Response</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- General\n    : Via, Connection 등의 항목\n\n- Response\n    : 헤더로써 응답의 내용을 구체화 시키는 항목\n\n- Entity\n    : 본문이 적용된 내용에 관련된 항목</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"이런-값들이-있어요-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%9F%B0-%EA%B0%92%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%B4-%EC%9E%88%EC%96%B4%EC%9A%94-1\" aria-label=\"이런 값들이 있어요 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이런 값들이 있어요!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Content-Type : 바디 데이터의 타입\nContent-Length : 바디 데이터 크기\nSet-Cookie : 쿠키 설정</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"body-의-type\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#body-%EC%9D%98-type\" aria-label=\"body 의 type permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Body 의 Type!</h2>\n<h3 id=\"--request-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--request-2\" aria-label=\"  request 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Request</h3>\n<p>Form</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: URLEncoded 방식 / 쿼리 문자열 (Query String)\n  &gt; application/x-www-form-urlencoded</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">    주소값 맨 뒤에 &#39;?aa=sdf&amp;bb=efe&#39; 와 같이\n    쿼리 구분자인 ? 의 뒤에, 키=값 의 형태로 내용이 제공됨!</code></pre></div>\n<p>JSON</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: 키와 값으로 이루어진 객체\n  &gt; application/json</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">    {\n      &quot;과일&quot;:&quot;망고&quot;,\n      &quot;개수&quot;:5\n    }</code></pre></div>\n<p>Multi-Part</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: 이진파일을 전송할 때, 하나의 메세지 바디에 파트를 나눠서 작성\n  &gt; 파일 업로드와 같은 통신에 사용\n  &gt; 파트 구분자로 boundary 를 사용\n  &gt; multipart/form-data: boundary=frontier</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"--response-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#--response-2\" aria-label=\"  response 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>- Response</h3>\n<p>HTML</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: HTML 문서 형태\n  &gt; 응답의 내용이 HTML 문서로 제공되어야 할 때</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  예를 들면,\n    &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n    &lt;HEAD&gt;\n      &lt;title&gt;예시&lt;/title&gt;\n    &lt;/HEAD&gt;\n    &lt;BODY&gt;\n      &lt;h1&gt;예시입니다!&lt;/h1&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;예시라구요!&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;/BODY&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>JSON</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: 키와 값으로 이루어진 객체\n  &gt; application/json</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  예를 들면,\n    {\n      &quot;과일&quot;:&quot;망고&quot;,\n      &quot;개수&quot;:5\n    }</code></pre></div>\n<p>Octet Stream</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">: 패킷, 청크 단위로 쪼개어진 이진파일\n  &gt; 스트리밍이나 다운로드와 같은 통신에 사용</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h1 id=\"위의-설명들을-참고해서-내용을-보세요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%84%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C-%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9%EC%9D%84-%EB%B3%B4%EC%84%B8%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"위의 설명들을 참고해서 내용을 보세요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>위의 설명들을 참고해서 내용을 보세요!</h1>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"request-의-모양새\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#request-%EC%9D%98-%EB%AA%A8%EC%96%91%EC%83%88\" aria-label=\"request 의 모양새 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Request 의 모양새</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">POST /payment-sync HTTP/1.1\n\nAccept: application/json\nAccept-Encoding: gzip, deflate\nConnection: keep-alive\nContent-Length: 83\nContent-Type: application/json\nHost: intropython.com\nUser-Agent: HTTPie/0.9.3\n\n{\n  &quot;imp_uid&quot;: &quot;imp_1234567890&quot;,\n  &quot;merchant_uid&quot;: &quot;order_id_8237352&quot;,\n  &quot;status&quot;: &quot;paid&quot;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"response-의-모양새\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#response-%EC%9D%98-%EB%AA%A8%EC%96%91%EC%83%88\" aria-label=\"response 의 모양새 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Response 의 모양새</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found\n\nConnection: close\nContent-Length: 1573\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8\nDate: Mon, 20 Aug 2018 07:59:05 GMT\n\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html lang=en&gt;\n&lt;meta charset=utf-8&gt;\n&lt;meta name=viewport content=&quot;initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, width=device-width&quot;&gt;\n&lt;title&gt;Error 404 (Not Found)!!1&lt;/title&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n  생략 {\n    했습 : 니다;\n  }\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;a href=//www.google.com/&gt;&lt;span id=logo aria-label=Google&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;404.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;ins&gt;That’s an error.&lt;/ins&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The requested URL &lt;code&gt;/payment-sync&lt;/code&gt; was not found on this server.  &lt;ins&gt;That’s all we know.&lt;/ins&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"이렇게-http-통신은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%A0%87%EA%B2%8C-http-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"이렇게 http 통신은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이렇게, HTTP 통신은</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">요청과 응답을 주고받는다는 특징이 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"저희가-하고있는-통신은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%80%ED%9D%AC%EA%B0%80-%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"저희가 하고있는 통신은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>저희가 하고있는 통신은,</h2>\n<h2 id=\"저런-모양의-정보를-주고받는-행위에요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%80%EB%9F%B0-%EB%AA%A8%EC%96%91%EC%9D%98-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B3%A0%EB%B0%9B%EB%8A%94-%ED%96%89%EC%9C%84%EC%97%90%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"저런 모양의 정보를 주고받는 행위에요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>저런 모양의 정보를 주고받는 행위에요!</h2>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/req_res","tagSlugs":["/tag/web/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-28","description":"HTTP 의 요청과 응답에 대한 글입니다.","tags":["web"],"title":"요청과 응답 ?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/req_res"}}}